            <title>[LU-12375] lnet should start after opa service</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12375</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lnet.service should list opa.service in the After line so that it starts after opa but more importantly, it is stopped BEFORE opa is disabled.&#160; This prevents client from hanging on unmount with OmniPath.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
